# Storage Area Network (SAN) - рд╣рд┐рдВрджреА + English

## ЁЯФ╕ What is SAN? (SAN рдХреНрдпрд╛ рд╣реЛрддрд╛ рд╣реИ?)

**English:**  
A Storage Area Network (SAN) is a high-speed network that connects storage devices (like hard drives) to servers. It allows multiple servers to access the same storage as if it were their own local disk.

**Hindi:**  
