## ЁЯФ╣ Why use SAN? (SAN рдХрд╛ рдЙрдкрдпреЛрдЧ рдХреНрдпреЛрдВ рдХрд░реЗрдВ?)

**English:**
- Centralized storage management  
- Fast data access and transfer  
- Scalability (easy to add more storage)  
- High performance and availability  

