ЁЯФР Amazon Encryption aur KMS Key тАУ рдЖрд╕рд╛рди рднрд╛рд╖рд╛ рдореЗрдВ (Hindi)
ЁЯФ╕ Encryption kya hota hai?
Encryption ek process hai jisme data ko aise code mein badal diya jata hai jo sirf authorized user hi samajh sake. Ye data ko secure banata hai.

ЁЯФ╣ Mool (original) data тЮбя╕П encrypted data (code ban gaya)

ЁЯФ╕ Amazon KMS (Key Management Service) kya hai?
AWS KMS (Key Management Service) ek managed service hai jo encryption ke liye keys banata, use karta, aur secure karta hai.

ЁЯСЙ Simple shabdon mein:
KMS ek digital locker jaisa hai jisme aapki encryption keys rakhi hoti hain. Jab aapko data encrypt/decrypt karna ho, aap KMS se us key ka use karte ho.

ЁЯУж Daily Life Example (Hindi):
ЁЯЫНя╕П Example: Online Shopping Password
Socho aapne Amazon pe shopping ki aur apna credit card number save kiya.

Encryption kya karta hai?
Card number ko unreadable format mein badal deta hai (so hackers canтАЩt read it).

KMS Key kya karti hai?
Wo secret chabi hai jo us encrypted data ko wapas original mein badal sakti hai (jab aap payment karte ho).

ЁЯФР Sirf Amazon (authorized system) ke paas wo chabi hoti hai. Aapka data safe hai.

ЁЯФР Amazon Encryption and KMS Key тАУ Simple English
ЁЯФ╕ What is Encryption?
Encryption is the process of converting readable data into unreadable code to protect it from unauthorized access.

ЁЯФ╣ Plain data тЮбя╕П Encrypted (locked) data

ЁЯФ╕ What is AWS KMS (Key Management Service)?
AWS KMS is a managed service that creates, stores, and manages the keys used for encryption and decryption.

ЁЯСЙ In simple words:
KMS is like a digital key locker that safely stores the keys used to lock (encrypt) and unlock (decrypt) your data.

ЁЯУж Daily Life Example (English):
ЁЯЫНя╕П Example: Online Shopping Password
Suppose you shop on Amazon and save your credit card number.

What does Encryption do?
It changes your card number into a secret code so no one can understand it.

What does the KMS key do?
It is the secret key that can unlock the code (decrypt) when needed during a payment.

ЁЯФР Only Amazon (the authorized system) has the key stored in KMS. So your data is safe.

ЁЯФС Summary Table
Concept	Hindi Explanation	English Explanation
Encryption	Data ko secret code mein badalna	Turn readable data into unreadable form
KMS Key	Wo chabi jo data ko unlock/lock karne ke kaam aati hai	A key used to encrypt/decrypt the data
KMS Service	Keys ko manage aur secure karne ki AWS service	AWS service to manage and secure the keys

